4. Active voice. Third person. No first-person pronouns.
5. Banned words: passionate, results-driven, team player, synergy, dynamic, go-getter, leverage, cutting-edge.
6. Output plain text only (no LaTeX, no quotes, no labels, no markdown).` },
    { role: 'user', content: `SOURCE Summary:
${summarySrc}

RESUME (full context):
${src}

JD:
${jd}

Target role: ${data.jobTitle} at ${data.company}` }
  ]
};
return [{ json: { ...data, _groqBody: JSON.stringify(body) } }];

